{"tid":2314854,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"震驚！這個國家竟然通過徵收「一次性富豪稅」，收取富人總資產高達5.25%資產稅！","createTime":"2020-12-06T21:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T05:19:00.000Z","uid":201299,"like":217,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"32bfd17af19ec10ecc7d16190f2e5c10e0568a42","tid":2314854,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T21:46:46.000Z","msg":"阿根廷政府於當地時間4日通過「富豪稅」，該稅項將用於支付新冠疫情中的醫療開支。<br />\n<br />\n阿根廷參議院以42票贊成、26票反對，通過這項法案。該法案計畫向資產超過2億比索（約1900萬港元）的富豪徵收一次性的稅款，徵收稅率最高為3.5%，而海外資產稅率則最高為5.25%。<br />\n<br />\n當局計畫透過這筆稅款來幫助經濟，希望可以籌出3000億比索(約285億港元)的資金來面對疫情的衝擊，稅收中的20％將用於購買醫療用品、20％將撥給中小企、20％將放於教育、15％用於社會發展，及25％投入於天然氣項目。<br />\n<br />\n阿根廷約有4400萬人口，但確診數已超過146萬。病例數世界排名第九，南美洲只僅次於巴西，病毒衝擊讓國內本就悽慘的失業率、貧窮率和政府負債都「節節高升」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1942782/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E9%98%BF%E6%A0%B9%E5%BB%B7%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E-%E5%AF%8C%E8%B1%AA%E7%A8%85-%E7%94%A8%E6%96%BC%E6%87%89%E4%BB%98%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E9%96%8B%E6%94%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1942782%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E9%2598%25BF%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E5%25BB%25B7%25E9%2580%259A%25E9%2581%258E-%25E5%25AF%258C%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E7%25A8%2585-%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2596%25BC%25E6%2587%2589%25E4%25BB%2598%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25AF&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2kngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=a53edd41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1942782%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E9%2598%25BF%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E5%25BB%25B7%25E9%2580%259A%25E9%2581%258E-%25E5%25AF%258C%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E7%25A8%2585-%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2596%25BC%25E6%2587%2589%25E4%25BB%2598%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25AF&h=4ef44c46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1942782/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E9%98%BF%E6%A0%B9%E5%BB%B7%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E-%E5%AF%8C%E8%B1%AA%E7%A8%85-%E7%94%A8%E6%96%BC%E6%87%89%E4%BB%98%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E9%96%8B%E6%94%AF</a>"},{"pid":"4c751b17b48f0740fa3715c64ded351406e917c6","tid":2314854,"uid":63669,"like":245,"dislike":20,"score":225,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T21:50:46.000Z","msg":"垃圾民粹國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嚇走投資者未來只會更加窮"},{"pid":"654d3b894a117e1b497c1818e05097e2ae563ca3","tid":2314854,"uid":302151,"like":144,"dislike":3,"score":141,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T21:53:05.000Z","msg":"支那放毒 但要自己人埋單"},{"pid":"12276b486a6a94e7ee46935763122c0cd283cc42","tid":2314854,"uid":201299,"like":185,"dislike":4,"score":181,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T22:00:57.000Z","msg":"阿根廷雖然人口有成4400萬<br />\n但係總資產超過1900萬港紙得12000人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d999110c13c7e46725f7ade4982bf380ca30a627","tid":2314854,"uid":51677,"like":69,"dislike":1,"score":68,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T22:05:53.000Z","msg":"班球星係咪個個都要交<br />\n美c咁疊水咁咪交好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915668b1db48fd512ee898c7a4510efa0f498866","tid":2314854,"uid":1275,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"12276b486a6a94e7ee46935763122c0cd283cc42","tid":2314854,"uid":201299,"like":185,"dislike":4,"score":181,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T22:00:57.000Z","msg":"阿根廷雖然人口有成4400萬<br />\n但係總資產超過1900萬港紙得12000人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T22:06:11.000Z","msg":"球王美欺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/